y using Chainlink price feeds and position imbalances in the GLP pool. Long-heavy positions pay funding to shorts when WLD trades above oracle price, while shorts pay longs during bearish sentiment. The oracle-based system reduces manipulation risk but can create arbitrage gaps versus centralized exchanges during high volatility periods. Funding payments settle automatically every hour directly to trader positions."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
